vlib_kalmanFilter_4x12_F32 Struct Reference

#include <VLIB_kalmanFilter.h>

Detailed Description

Structure defining the state of the Kalman filter for the F32, 4x12 (4-Dimension Observation x 12-Dimension State Vectors) variant.

int32_t vlib_kalmanFilter_4x12_F32::scaleFactor

Scales the matrix M = (H*P1*H' + R) to ensure that its inverse does not overflow 32 bits. The scaling is done by right shifting each element of M by the quantity assigned to scaleFactor. The computed inverse is then scaled back to ensure the correct result based on the identity inv(M) = inv(M/k)/k
